Who we are

Adept4 delivers IT as a Service to small and medium-sized businesses across the UK. ITaaS provides you with exactly the amount of technology to support your need in accordance with business requirements, billed on a monthly basis, based on what is consumed. 
Effectively, we provide you with Enterprise-level IT on a PAYG basis.
ITaaSTechnologies 






One single trusted provider

Critically we underpin our delivery method with our Service offering a 24x7 UK response team, strategic consulting, professional services and software development to provide exactly what organisations need from IT at any given time. Whether an infrastructure is based on legacy or emerging technologies, we will ensure organisations have the flexibility, agility and cost efficiencies required to run their businesses effectively, all through one single trusted provider.
Adept4 is a public company quoted on the AIM market of the London Stock Exchange. The Company is headquartered in Warrington, with offices in Leeds, Aberdeen and Brighton
ServicesSupport 






Our customers

We are customer and people centric, an organisation you can grow with, focused entirely on becoming our customers’ trusted local IT expert. We work with c.800 small and medium- sized businesses. Our consistent growth and strength is enabled by an amazing 95% customer retention rate, and by 70% of our revenues being both contracted and recurring revenues.
Case studies 





Some of our customers

Baywater (new)
 

Boundless by CSMA (new)
 

CRC (new)
 

Frederic Robinson (new)
 

MerseyLink (new)
 

Schofield Insurance (new)
 







Our partnerships

In the delivery of our solutions and services we work with and leverage only leading edge technologies and partners. As Tier 1 Microsoft Cloud Service Providers (CSP) in the UK, our strong relationship with Microsoft enables us to embrace the current and emerging product suite to fully leverage what is offered today, ensuring we know exactly what is in the roadmap for tomorrow and in turn offering to our customers the best fit solution to their current and impending challenges.
In the telecoms arena we partner with leading vendors like Mitel, where we are one of the only Gold partners accredited in the UK to sell both the enterprise MX1 and 400 systems. 
Other Tier 1 technology partnerships include a select number of technology leaders such as Cisco, Veeam, VMware, Fortinet, Sage, and Trend Micro.
 





